@META
dir: skillsPraut
updated: 2026-04-15
files: 6 (package.json, tsconfig.json, bun.lock, README.md, .gitignore)
stack: Remotion 4, React 19, @remotion/{bundler,cli,fonts,google-fonts,lottie,shapes,three,transitions}, TypeScript 5.4

@EXPORTS
package.json → name: @praut/remotion-skill v1.0.0 (private)
tsconfig.json → ESNext + JSX react-jsx + strict + path alias @/*→src/*

@VARS_CONSTANTS
SCRIPTS: dev=remotion studio | render=remotion render | build=remotion bundle | typecheck=tsc --noEmit | extract-glyphs=node scripts/extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs

@PROCESSES
dev: bun dev → remotion studio → localhost:3000 preview
render: bun render <CompositionId> out/<name>.mp4
glyph-refresh: bun run extract-glyphs → regenerates src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: src/ (entry) | skills/ (claude skill) | scripts/ | public/ (fonts+logos)
external runtime: remotion@^4, react@^19, react-dom@^19, all @remotion/* @^4
external dev: typescript@^5.4, @types/react(@^19), @types/react-dom@^19

@STANDARDS
- Package manager: bun (bun.lock) — NOT yarn, NOT npm
- Entry point: src/index.ts → registerRoot(RemotionRoot)
- Path alias: @/* → src/*
- Font loading happens once in Root.tsx (Montserrat + IBM Plex Mono + Phosphor)
- Private package — never published to npm

@WARNINGS
- node_modules/, out/, renders/ .gitignored (large artifacts)
